, 人工唔係神級高, 女人先岩做"},{"pid":"fd3d4e40c8045f53f755049b074d4c9e9814534c","tid":303270,"uid":85093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過往係有d RD 學生係 non jupas 入嘅，不過second degree 有幾多就唔清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都唔少<br />\n但through jupas多D"},{"pid":"880f742eb0008bba605be9b85d0e7ccb098c6001","tid":303270,"uid":85093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過往係有d RD 學生係 non jupas 入嘅，不過second degree 有幾多就唔清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都唔少<br />\n但through jupas多D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n指second degree用番jupas"},{"pid":"3ed9428c033f3cda97c5e03670bec66b33fbe6ee","tid":303270,"uid":125831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今年u grad<br />\n都有諗過考多次dse<br />\n不過first choice係想試下過唔過到外國讀<br />\n其實最難係放低左個考試模式四年<br />\n同埋真係讀既話會同人差左四年經驗同人工<br />\n仲有邊番工邊溫書都真係唔易</blockquote><br />\n我因為First deg係pure science所以某程度上DSE啲science科我好易handle得到<br />\n至於你話差左經驗同人工...我就覺得四年時間同終生既職業相比，都博得過"},{"pid":"78582d107dd02056d4870e96bf4f2884076f412a","tid":303270,"uid":96535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點同路法先</blockquote><br />\n報左jupas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}